Dexy is software for document automation.

http://dexy.it
http://blog.dexy.it

For examples using dexy:
http://bitbucket.org/ananelson/dexy-examples

For detailed installation instructions:
http://bitbucket.org/ananelson/dexy-install


Dexy should work on Python 2.5-Python 2.7. Dexy will not work on Windows due to
dependency on pexpect but we are working on removing this restriction, in the
mean time if you are working on Windows then you can run Dexy within a Linux
VM.

